OL,3,CRioter cries in court after admitting
OL,4,C'active role' in attack on black man
OL,6,FA rioter cried in court as he admitted
OL,7,Fplaying "an active role" in disorder
OL,8,Fwhich saw a black man attacked by a
OL,9,F"large group of far-right protesters"
OL,10,Fin Manchester.
OL,12,FLiam Ryan, 28, of Thirkleby Royd,
OL,13,FBradford, pleaded guilty to violent
OL,14,Fdisorder at Manchester Magistrates'
OL,15,FCourt on Wednesday.
OL,17,FProsecutor Laura Peers said there had
OL,18,Fbeen a number of "large-scale
OL,19,Fdisturbances" in Piccadilly Gardens on
OL,20,F3 August, and Ryan had travelled from
OL,21,FWest Yorkshire to participate.
