OL,3,CRioter cries in court after admitting
OL,4,C'active role' in attack on black man
OL,6,FMs Peers said a "large group of far-
OL,7,Fright protesters" were seen engaging
OL,8,Fin an "altercation with one black
OL,9,Fmale", which was filmed and uploaded
OL,10,Fon social media.
OL,12,FThe prosecutor said the footage,
OL,13,Ffilmed by a member of the public,
OL,14,Fshowed "a black male being confronted
OL,15,Fby a large group of white males".
OL,17,FMs Peers said Ryan had "played an
OL,18,Factive role in the disorder", adding:
OL,19,F"He was seen on the footage aiming a
OL,20,Fpunch towards the male involved."
