OL,6,FDistrict Judge Jane Hamilton remanded
OL,7,FRyan, who was shaking as he wiped
OL,8,Ftears away with a tissue after
OL,9,Fpleading guilty to violent disorder,
OL,10,Finto custody.
OL,12,FShe ordered him to appear at
OL,13,FManchester Crown Court on 14 August.
OL,15,FMore than 400 arrests have been made
OL,16,Fand around 100 people have been
OL,17,Fcharged in connection with the
OL,18,Fdisorder in the wake of the Southport
OL,19,Fstabbing.
